{"type":"message","id":"1dcb4683","parentId":"8f8a9b14","timestamp":"2026-05-26T05:31:20.175Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e674f2348bcb4c041d103403df\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-26 13:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\"\n}\n```\n\n**GMV MAX 投流的逻辑 ROI **\n\n【这段视频是关于跨境电商中ROI（投资回报率）和广告跑量的讲解，核心内容如下：\n\n### 一、核心问题解答\n为什么有的商家ROI设2都跑不动，而有的设8却能爆单？\n这不是玄学，而是由**ECPM（千次展示收益）**的底层逻辑决定的。ECPM公式为：`ECPM = 出价 × 预估点击率 × 预估转化率 × 1000`。在GMVMAX体系中，**出价约等于ROI**，但出价不是唯一变量。如果内容、产品不行，即使出价（ROI）再高也跑不动量。\n\n### 二、关键指标解析\n1. **GPM（千次曝光成交金额）**：\n 公式为 `GPM = 转化率 × 客单价`，它直接对应系统后台的**预估点击率和预估转化率**。GPM越高，系统给的**预估排名越高**，进而ECPM越高，拿量能力就越强。\n2. **影响GPM的因素**：\n - **客单价**：客单价越高，GPM基数越大。比如同样1000次曝光，卖50元的比卖20元的GPM基数大。\n - **转化率**：转化率越高，GPM乘数越大。比如同样产品，转化率5%的比2%的GPM乘数大。\n\n### 三、优化方向\n要提高跑量能力和ROI，需优化**客单价**和**转化率**：\n- 提高客单价：可通过产品迭代、组合、优化SKU等方式。\n- 提高转化率：可通过打磨视频内容、优化产品卖点等方式。"}],"timestamp":1779773480056}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ab01094","parentId":"1dcb4683","timestamp":"2026-05-26T05:31:45.772Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a question about TikTok Ads GMV MAX bidding strategy and ROI logic. The user shared a video transcript about ECPM, GPM, and what determines ad delivery performance.\n\nLet me provide a clear, practical summary based on the content shared. The sender (HALEI) seems to be sharing educational content about advertising strategy. As TK投流专家, I should respond with insights relevant to their role.\n\nThe key points from the video:\n1. ECPM = Bid × CTR × CVR × 1000\n2. In GMV MAX system, bid ≈ ROI target\n3. GPM (Gross Merchandise Volume per mille) = CVR × AOV\n\n\n4. Both AOV and conversion rate feed into the ECPM algorithm and determine whether ads can actually run\n5. If conversion metrics are weak, raising the ROI target won't help—the ad simply won't deliver\n\nThis means the real optimization path is improving the product and content quality first, since those drive the conversion metrics that the algorithm needs to function, and only then can you set ambitious ROI targets and expect them to work.\n","thinkingSignature":"44c0319538eaed2c504425259d5576e8797acc300976e32a10a7330377939600"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这段内容把 GMV MAX 的底层逻辑讲得很清楚。核心就一句话：\n\n**出价（ROI目标）只是 ECPM 的一个因子，内容和产品不行，再高的出价也拿不到量。**\n\n---\n\n### ECPM 公式\n\n```\nECPM = 出价 × 预估点击率 × 预估转化率 × 1000\n```\n\nGMV MAX 里**出价 ≈ 目标ROI**，但光调出价没用——如果 CTR 和 CVR 上不去，ECPM 垫底，平台压根不给你跑。\n\n---\n\n### GPM = 转化率 × 客单价\n\n这才是决定预估排名和拿量能力的核心。\n\n| 因子 | 怎么提升 |\n|------|----------|\n| **客单价** | 产品迭代、组合套餐、优化SKU |\n| **转化率** | 视频内容打磨、产品卖点提炼 |\n\n客单价高 → GPM 基数大 → 预估排名高 → ECPM 高 → 拿量能力强\n\n转化率高 → GPM 乘数大 → 同理\n\n---\n\n### 实际投放中的应用\n\n当你说 \"ROI 设 2 跑不动\" 的时候，真实原因往往是：\n\n1. **GPM 太低** — 产品客单价低 + 转化差，ECPM 竞争力不足\n2. **素材衰减** — 同样的产品，跑久了 CTR/CVR 下降，ECPM 跟着跌\n3. **定向太窄** — 人群包小，流量池有限，平台优化空间受限\n\n反过来，**\"ROI 设 8 还能爆\"** 的计划，往往是产品+素材本身 GPM 就高，平台主动给它放量。\n\n---\n\n### 建议\n\n如果你的计划 ROI 目标设高了跑不动，别急着降 ROI。先看后台：\n- 这条计划的 **GPM 预估** 是多少\n- 素材的 **CTR/CVR** 趋势是否在下掉\n- 客单价有没有拉上去的空间\n\n**数据调优，不是凭经验猜。** 要不要我帮你看一下具体计划数据，分析一下哪块拖了后腿？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44852,"output":654,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45506,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779773480343,"responseId":"06646329e20626036a238ba3376a376f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4969319e","parentId":"6ab01094","timestamp":"2026-05-26T05:40:16.354Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e676d0b1484c321eef18e910ff\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-26 13:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\"\n}\n```\n\n视频里的核心公式：ROI = GPM ÷ ECPM，而GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000"}],"timestamp":1779774016227}}
