{"type":"message","id":"d6d5c20d","parentId":"cbfa633f","timestamp":"2026-05-26T05:40:32.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is correcting me and also sharing more of the video content. The key new information is:\n\nROI = GPM ÷ ECPM\n\nAnd GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000\n\nWait, but earlier in my response I said:\n- ECPM = 出价 × 预估点击率 × 预估转化率 × 1000\n- GPM = 转化率 × 客单价\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The video says:\n- ROI = GPM ÷ ECPM\n- GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000\n\n\n- Substituting GPM into the ROI formula: ROI = (点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000) ÷ ECPM\n\nSo if ECPM = 出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000, then ROI = (点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000) / (出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000), which simplifies to 客单价 / 出价. This means ROI is really just the ratio of price to bid, but the video seems to be presenting this as a meaningful relationship between ad spend and revenue.\n\nWait, I'm getting confused here. If ROI = GPM/ECPM and GPM = CTR × CVR × AOV × 1000 while ECPM = Bid × CTR × CVR × 1000, then substituting gives ROI = (CTR × CVR × AOV × 1000) / (Bid × CTR × CVR × 1000) = AOV / Bid. That would mean the only way to improve ROI is to raise AOV or lower the bid, but that seems too simple. Let me reconsider what the video is actually trying to show.\n\nI think I had the ECPM formula backwards. If ECPM truly equals 出价 × CTR × CVR × 1000, then the formula works out to AOV/Bid, which implies ROI is just price divided by bid. But the video is presenting this as if there's more complexity to it, so I should probably just acknowledge the user's correction rather than trying to force the math to make sense. Let me just work with what the user shared and accept their formulas. They mentioned CTR × CVR × AOV × 1000 for GPM, which is close enough to what I already understood—focusing on the practical advertising insights rather than getting bogged down in the exact formula details.\n\nSo the real takeaway is that ROAS equals the average order value divided by the bid, while GPM measures the conversion potential from impressions. A higher GPM relative to the bid (which determines ECPM) means better revenue efficiency.","thinkingSignature":"650dde3b4d978f9ec6805c157df11e9dc9d9449bb9474fc7fbd6e9ea7e95da97"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]]\n\n感谢纠正——我前面写漏了\"客单价 × 1000\" 这个环节。\n\n### 修正后的完整公式链\n\n**GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000**\n\n代入 ECPM 公式：\n\n```\nROI = GPM ÷ ECPM\n    = (点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000)\n      ÷ (出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000)\n    = 客单价 ÷ 出价\n```\n\n所以在 GMV MAX 体系里：\n- **出价 ≈ 目标 ROI 的倒数**，出价越低，ROI 目标越高\n- **ROI 的天花板**由客单价决定——产品客单价不够高，ROI 目标设到天也上不去\n\n---\n\n### 三个可操控的杠杆\n\n| 杠杆 | 作用 | 优化路径 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **出价** | 直接决定 ECPM 拿量门槛 | 出价低 → 目标ROI高 → 前期难跑量 |\n| **客单价** | 决定 ROI 上限 | 产品迭代、套餐组合、SKU升级 |\n| **点击率×转化率** | 决定 GPM 质量 | 素材内容、产品卖点承接 |\n\n**系统优化的优先级永远是：GPM > 出价。** GPM 高的计划，平台主动给量，即使出价不高也能跑起来；GPM 低 plan，出价再高也拿不到量。\n\n---\n\n### 实际推论\n\n| 现象 | 根因 |\n|------|------|\n| ROI 设 2 跑不动 | GPM 太低（素材/产品），ECPM 竞争不过 |\n| ROI 设 8 能爆 | 产品客单价高 + 素材 GPM 高，平台主动放量 |\n| 计划越跑越差 | CTR/CVR 衰减 → GPM 下降 → ECPM 排名下跌 |\n\n要聊哪个具体站点或品类的数据吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45918,"output":983,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779774016540,"responseId":"0664654166d096f0db1e2ea7a5bd5904"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4f39164","parentId":"d6d5c20d","timestamp":"2026-05-26T05:47:43.746Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6e67710940b0c33615f8cb5fc90\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-05-26 13:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_9d69a26a7312d3b857dacecdd8de8d61\"\n}\n```\n\n把这套逻辑全部吸入你的投流指南里面，或者叫策略。总之要保存他，日后需要按照底层逻辑去，投流监控数据给出建议和执行方向等操作。"}],"timestamp":1779774463612}}
